    'description' => 'Export the results of a SQL query (from any SQLite database in the workspace) as a formatted Markdown table. Useful for composing SQL queries into reports, documentation, or feeding results to scheduled_report. Pure read-only — never modifies the source database. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
